        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-primary font-bold text-xl border border-white/10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">D</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Dorian</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-primary/70 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Security Lead</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-textMuted">Especialista en ciberseguridad y servidores. El guardián de la infraestructura.</p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- CARD MIGUEL -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-surface border border-white/5 rounded-xl hover:border-secondary/30 transition-all group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-secondary font-bold text-xl border border-white/10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">M</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Miguel</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-secondary/70 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Frontend Lead</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-textMuted">Obsesionado con la velocidad, el diseño y la experiencia de usuario (UX).</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>